Usage: create_histogram_png [-help] [-height <integer>] -name <string>
                            [-width <integer>]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-height <integer>  # PNG file height (int, optional, min=1, max=10000)
-name <string>     # PNG file name (string, required)
-width <integer>   # PNG file widtd (int, optional, min=1, max=10000)